Package: xsp2
Title: Chi-Square Periodogram
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
  person("Jared", "Stevens", email = "jpsteve1@uno.edu", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph")),
  person("Hitoshi", "Iuchi", role = c("ctb", "cph")),
  person("Rikuhiro G.", "Yamada", role = "ctb"))
Maintainer: Jared Stevens <jpsteve1@uno.edu>
Description: Computes chi-square periodograms to predict circadian periods and assess statistical significance of rhythmicity in time series data (Sokolove & Bushell, 1978) <doi:10.1016/0022-5193(78)90022-X>. This package builds upon and improves the original xsp package <https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=xsp> by supporting flexible binning and customizable period ranges.
